营协会发布《2023 中国连锁 TOP100》榜单，胖东来以 13 家门店 107 亿元的销售额排在榜单 46 位。于东来对此表示： 图片来源：视频截图 不少网友评论：「就该他发财！」「真诚才是必杀技」。也有网友调侃：「于东来又要为赚太多烦恼了。」 另据中证金牛座 11 月 27 日消息，2024 联商东来总裁班第三期课程在许昌举行前夕，名创优品集团创始人、董事会主席兼首席执行官叶国富到访，胖东来董事长于东来及高管团队与其会面。胖东来养活了超 300 个代购账号，有的一个月能卖近 250 万元！创始人于东来发文提醒"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-95d060aaa3e83d9ee275661924637faf_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5459136213"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIkPz7m863obMvEAMaCTExMjA2ODMzNiDX3qS6BjAAOJACQAdyCjU0NTkxMzYyMTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1732907989.62452", "card_id": "Q_5324478064", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "既然无人机群无法拦截，那么未来战争还需要航母吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5324478064"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIkPz7m863obMvEAMaCTExMjA0MTM3MSCH+py6BjAAOExACHIKNTMyNDQ3ODA2NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1732907989.62664", "card_id": "Q_443259905", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《大明王朝 1566》中六必居的老板，时时刻刻被锦衣卫给监视着，那他怎么做生意？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "顾客看到锦衣卫就像老鼠看到猫一样，也不会有人买这家酱菜，那这家六必居如何维持？老板又不能关张停业，看他整天对着锦衣卫颤颤巍巍的，应该是备受折磨吧…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-39d0e5d2386555d6c3f020b3796d7060_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5